oracleReaderQuery.value:
select * from BETADATA.STATIONLOCATIONS
where SLOC_MODIFIED >= TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') 
AND SLOC_MODIFIED < TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')
AND VPD_ID in @{item().vpd_list}

select * from BETADATA.STATIONSETTINGSGROUP
where SSG_MODIFIED>= TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') 
AND SSG_MODIFIED< TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')
AND VPD_ID in @{item().vpd_list}

select  /*+INDEX(t,STATIONSETTINGS_MODIFIED) */* from BETADATA.STATIONSETTINGS t
where SS_MODIFIED >= TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') 
AND SS_MODIFIED < TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')
AND VPD_ID in @{item().vpd_list}

select /*+INDEX(t,POSITEMS_MODIFIED) */ * from BETADATA.POSITEMS t
where POSI_MODIFIED >= TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') 
AND POSI_MODIFIED < TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')

select t1.*
from betadata.positemtaxes t1
join betadata.positems t2 on t1.vpd_id=t2.vpd_id and t1.posi_id=t2.posi_id
where POSI_MODIFIED >= TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')
AND POSI_MODIFIED < TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')
AND t1.VPD_ID in @{item().vpd_list}

select  /*+INDEX(t,SALEITEMS_MODIFIED) */ * from BETADATA.SALEITEMS t
where SAI_MODIFIED>= TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') 
AND SAI_MODIFIED< TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')
AND VPD_ID in @{item().vpd_list}

select  /*+INDEX(t1,SPL_SPL_ACTIVE) */  t1.*
from betadata.serviceproviderlocations t1
join betadata.serviceproviders t2 on t1.sp_id=t2.sp_id 
where corp_id=11500  /*Planet Fitness*/

oracleReaderQuery.value:
select * from BETADATA.TIMETRACKINGBREAKS
where TTB_MODIFIED >= TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') 
AND TTB_MODIFIED < TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')
AND VPD_ID in @{item().vpd_list}

select * from BETADATA.TIMETRACKING
where TT_MODIFIED >= TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') 
AND TT_MODIFIED < TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') 
AND  tt_clock_in > TO_DATE('2017-01-01','YYYY-MM-DD') 
AND TT_CLOCK_IN_ALTERED > TO_DATE('2017-01-01','YYYY-MM-DD') 
AND TT_CLOCK_OUT > TO_DATE('2017-01-01','YYYY-MM-DD') 
AND TT_CLOCK_OUT_ALTERED >  TO_DATE('2017-01-01','YYYY-MM-DD')
AND VPD_ID in  @{item().vpd_list}
